text: Pollenfeld is a municipality in the district of Eichstätt in Bavaria in Germany. ==Division of Pollenfeld== Districts: Pollenfeld with Wörmersdorf, Seuversholz with Ziegelhütte, Sornhüll with Götzelshard, Wachenzell with Ziegelhütte, Weigersdorf and Preith. ==Geography== Pollenfeld is in the Ingolstadt region, 8 km (approx. 5 miles) north of the district seat (Kreisstadt) of Eichstätt in the Franconian Jura mountains. ==References== Category:Eichstätt (district)
title: Pollenfeld
